## 📊 OUTPUT INTERPRETATION

Each row in CSV represents:

* One parameter configuration
* Fully converged Monte Carlo result

Example:

| carrier-distance | final-p | final-duration-mean | runs-used | MOE   |
| ---------------- | ------- | ------------------- | --------- | ----- |
| 50               | 0.72    | 41                  | 312       | 0.049 |

